{"tid":1028502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣有兩條女叫停人請食飯","createTime":"2019-02-19T14:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T15:33:23.000Z","uid":82122,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0dca0c6bf7c0b2016463b55ac1c330ac259895","tid":1028502,"uid":82122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"今日21:15，有兩個女仔係青衣城外面（青敬路）靠停車場兩個馬路位，聖保祿村對開 ， 叫停我<br />\n<br />\n然後其中一個走過黎用普通話叫我請食飯（由於普通話能力有限，只記得幾個要點）<br />\n<br />\n佢話：不要介意，我是大陸人...來香港旅遊...我朋友（好似話冇錢）...想你請我們食飯<br />\n講到呢到我擰頭就走左<br />\n<br />\n1. 問都冇問我識唔識普通話，就一輪嘴講野，我似背書咁<br />\n2. 我一個人行路，見到我就眼神閃縮咁走過黎問野<br />\n3. 果個位係比較暗，而且人流少<br />\n4. Sor 冇圖<br />\n<br />\n睇各位勇士賽後檢討"},{"pid":"9036896bea43c8ef5da4323d66678f65b7a483ce","tid":1028502,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"整鬼人節目"},{"pid":"88a2c626ebb7e7716bae0c0988752a106c11ee32","tid":1028502,"uid":172825,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"你話你係警察 話佢地詐騙要拉佢地"},{"pid":"5341ed82ba2edde68fe56c7ea51aeae75b41ec5f","tid":1028502,"uid":53603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"我都係觀塘遇過<br />\n係咪一個矮肥一個高瘦?"},{"pid":"0906babeaefae1701d6468e114b1b0bd66af5978","tid":1028502,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"索唔索，索嘅可以借啲意抽下水"},{"pid":"99aed84937212b8171041cda44e40aec595fc943","tid":1028502,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"一聽大陸人就好撚介意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97195ef4ce01ab88d7fc628f0e9b89d50ee04b3","tid":1028502,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"4c3c8a6f857e47d0dbb6bd455ed601b55ecd4e37","tid":1028502,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:10:52.000Z","msg